params.markdown:
**Check Point Harmony Endpoint Overview**

**Overview**:

This dashboard is a health overview of Check Point Harmony Endpoint integration.

The dashboard provides general statistics and health of ingestion of logs from Check Point Harmony Endpoint.

It shows the details of logs with counts for selected time intervals. Top 5 "Users" and "Assets" with top 5 destination countries. The graph indicates accessed website categories that are blocked by endpoints with URL filtering.
